{"tid":1084902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警元朗掃淫窟大廈拉21人　包括3泰籍變性人","createTime":"2019-03-30T17:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T14:31:58.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6d876721d405942730727e58c6017de3c5a90d85","tid":1084902,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"元朗警區特別職務隊根據線報及深入調查後，昨日（30日）聯同新界北總區快速應變部隊、元朗警區雜項調查隊及特遣隊繼續進行一連串的掃黃行動。警員突擊搜查元朗壽富街一大廈，拘捕20名持護照的泰國籍男女，包括3名「人妖」及17女，1名持雙程證的內地女子，年齡介乎21至43歲，俱涉嫌違反逗留條件。<br />\n<br />\n警方於行動中檢獲一批避孕套及潤滑劑。所有被捕男女現正被扣留調查。警方行動仍在進行，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n元朗警區一直非常關注並致力打擊區內非法賣淫活動。根據現行法例，「違反逗留條件」一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款5萬元及監禁2年；「為不道德目的而唆使他人」一經定罪，最高罰款1萬元及監禁6個月。"},{"pid":"628261e20e0c0fededc5f7cd04ff2e77e10263fc","tid":1084902,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"唔好呀"},{"pid":"1c44b697600c9ca910bd94bae12453385be20fc6","tid":1084902,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地班黑警shit 眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555c7e5f243a204e6ef0c1a3dcab252d054e0b05","tid":1084902,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"仆街 尋日。。。"},{"pid":"ad0910e42325acadc1c6fbcc34e4eaa69305f080","tid":1084902,"uid":53695,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"包括3名「人妖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心啊雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfb5d225648dae172a3e49a771cb90943308ad2","tid":1084902,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:08:57.